{"tid":825481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片：山竹過後】沙嘴懲教所宿舍變廢墟　職員：千祈唔好入去","createTime":"2018-09-17T15:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T15:18:58.000Z","uid":6497,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"772f57d2890ecb462ea9fc09df99cde86b30e809","tid":825481,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180917/s00001/1537182268853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F1537182268853&d=BA7AskRBlxl8GurbDDSnvP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=35ab5dea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F1537182268853&h=a169d52c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180917/s00001/1537182268853</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00001/07f320dd0f2bc2c6335201c6cb4c459f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F07f320dd0f2bc2c6335201c6cb4c459f.jpg&h=6f503453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00001/07f3d729d541b34da12351b1361c762a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F07f3d729d541b34da12351b1361c762a.jpg&h=addae4ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強颱風「山竹」吹襲本港期間，在多處造成嚴重破壞，除市區有唐樓外牆倒塌外，大嶼山沙嘴懲教所亦不能倖免。所內一間職員營房外牆倒塌，旁邊路面下陷，營房地基亦恐被沖毀。有職員面對儼如廢墟的營房，提醒同袍：「千祈唔好入去呀呢棟嘢！」<br />\n<br />\n從網上流傳片段可見，營房外的石屎路已倒塌，地面一片泥濘，懲教署職員只能沿旁邊尚算完整的小路前進。一間營房其中一面外牆幾乎完全消失，只餘冷氣機只靠鐵架連接僅餘的外牆頂部，百葉簾及部分窗框搖搖欲墜。原放於室內的家俬雜物已被吹至一片混亂。有職員看見眼前情境，不禁嘆了一句：「打仗咩&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n旁邊另外兩間營房外的路面同樣已塌陷，現場滿目瘡痍。有懲教署職員指着其中一間營房，提醒同袍「千祈唔好入去呀呢棟嘢」，指營房地基已「真空晒，我都驚佢會冧」，有人回應要進去取回物品，之後便會離開。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署回覆《明報》查詢，指沙嘴懲教所一間職員營房在「山竹」吹襲時受破壞，其間並無懲教人員受傷。院所管方已即時安排受影響的懲教人員入住其他職員宿舍，及聯絡相關部門跟進。"},{"pid":"ef11563a3544fb5e909519931f53c843dd325c7b","tid":825481,"uid":127120,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"Thankyou sir 唔該同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec654d3630766b0d184b6c81aef1a7a2e07e7747","tid":825481,"uid":136994,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"阿Sir宿舍冇咗！<br />\n請你食多幾隻雞翼！"},{"pid":"9c411fe371cbd1982eb2f7e464a62eaaa662c533","tid":825481,"uid":61105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef11563a3544fb5e909519931f53c843dd325c7b","tid":825481,"uid":127120,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"Thankyou sir 唔該同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62382fc7785b74af5c1fd40278812b1580323950","tid":825481,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c411fe371cbd1982eb2f7e464a62eaaa662c533","tid":825481,"uid":61105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ef11563a3544fb5e909519931f53c843dd325c7b","tid":825481,"uid":127120,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"Thankyou sir 唔該同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065b38321d445303579b3c1442990d1ec9715f39","tid":825481,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62382fc7785b74af5c1fd40278812b1580323950","tid":825481,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c411fe371cbd1982eb2f7e464